snippet.title: MEATGRINDER - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1968710/MEATGRINDER/

MEATGRINDER is a brutal and fast-paced Roguelite FPS inspired by the best retro shooters and action movies. Fight hordes of punks in ever-changing environments, upgrade your weapons and skills and grind the meat.
